dde-shell-weather-plugin (1.6.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add KDE GeoIP (geoip.kde.org) as primary IP geolocation backend.
  * Location fallback chain is now: Qt Positioning -> KDE GeoIP -> ip-api -> Beijing.
  * KDE GeoIP uses HTTPS and MaxMind GeoLite2 data; ip-api retained as fallback.
  * Fix localised city names when using KDE GeoIP (now resolved via BigDataCloud).

 -- HualetWang <mr.asianwang@gmail.com>  Thu, 03 Apr 2026 14:00:00 +0800

